”; 
<emphasis box="[857,933,1094,1119]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="413">ibidem</emphasis>
, 1 male paratype (NMNH); [PERU or ARGENTINA] 
<emphasis box="[332,393,1132,1155]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="413">Rioja</emphasis>
, Sud América/ 
<emphasis box="[573,634,1132,1155]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="413">Rioja</emphasis>
