/ Figured by Linnavuori, 1961/ MMB[C]/ in 
<taxonomicName box="[544,717,1167,1192]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="413" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subFamily" subFamily="Neocoelidiinae">Neocoelidiinae</taxonomicName>
, D.A. Young [det.]/ Typus/ Collectio Dr. L. Melichar, Moravské Museum Brno, 1 male (MMBC). Note: although the specimen from Peru is labeled as a type, this is incorrect since, according to Distant (1908), the type of 
<taxonomicName authority="(Distant)" authorityName="Distant" baseAuthorityName="Distant" baseAuthorityYear="1908" box="[632,951,1239,1264]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Mesogonia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="413" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="apulia">
