<bibRefCitation author="Kramer" box="[541,707,1312,1337]" pageId="4" pageNumber="413" refString="Kramer, J. P. (1964) A generic revision of the leafhopper subfamily Neocoelidiinae (Homoptera: Cicadellidae). Proceedings of the United States National Museum, 115 (3484), 259 - 287. https: // doi. org / 10.5479 / si. 00963801.115 - 3484.259" type="journal article" year="1964">Kramer, 1964</bibRefCitation>
